      "nothing_better_than_coke_now_opt_5": "5",
      "nothing_better_than_coke_now_opt_6": "6",
      "nothing_better_than_coke_now_opt_7": "STRONGLY AGREE",
      "scoring_510302": "Scoring Procedure and InterpretationEach item is scored on a scale ranging from 1 for \"Strongly Disagree\" to 7 for \"Strongly Agree.\" The scores from items 1-3, 5, 6, and 8-10 are used as the raw scores. Items 4 and 7 should be reverse-scored (raw score = 8 minus reverse-keyed item score) (Heinz et al., 2006). A total score is obtained by averaging all items (Sussner et al., 2006)."
    }
